<mjml>
  <mj-head>
    <mj-style>
      h2, img, p { margin: 0; } td { padding-top: 0 !important; } p {
      margin-bottom: 10px; }
    </mj-style>
    <!-- <mj-font name="Roboto+Serif" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto+Serif" /> -->
    <mj-font
      name="Roboto+Serif"
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?faily=Roboto+Serif:ital,opsz,wght@0,8..144,100..900;1,8..144,100..900&display=swap"
    />
  </mj-head>
  <mj-body background-color="#f0f1f3">
    <mj-spacer height="15px"></mj-spacer>
    <!-- Header -->
    <mj-section background-color="#ffffff">
      <mj-column width="100%">
        <mj-spacer height="20px" />
        <mj-image
          padding="10px 12px"
          css-class="light_img"
          width="230px"
          src="https://www.pouringpotions.com/logo.png"
          href="https://www.pouringpotions.com"
          alt=""
        />

        <mj-divider
          border-width="1px"
          border-style="solid"
          border-color="lightgrey"
          padding="0px 12px"
        />
        <mj-text
          padding="10px 14px 8px 14px"
          font-family="Roboto+Serif"
          color="#000000"
        >
          <h2
            style="
              padding: 10px 0px;
              font-size: 18px;
              line-height: 1.5;
              margin-top: 2px;
              text-align: center;
            "
          >
            Your eye color can be a litmus test for your health!
          </h2>
          <p
            style="
              padding: 16px 0px 0px 0px;
              font-size: 16px;
              line-height: 1.5;
              text-align: right;
            "
          >
            <i
              >“My eyes are an ocean in which my dreams are reflected.”<br />
              -Anna M. Uhlich</i
            >
          </p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider
          border-width="1px"
          border-style="solid"
          border-color="lightgrey"
          padding="0px 12px"
        />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <!-- /Header -->

    <mj-spacer height="10px" />
    <mj-section background-color="#ffffff">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-spacer height="20px" />
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5">
            Do you know that our eyes not just reflect our dreams but also
            reflect our health? It reveals interesting facts about us that we
            hardly noticed before.
          </p>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5">
            Let’s discover the connection between your eye and your health.
          </p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-image
          border-radius="10px"
          padding="10px 14px "
          width="600px"
          src="https://www.pouringpotions.com/email/images/litmus-test.jpg"
          alt="Litmus test"
          href="https://www.pouringpotions.com"
        />
        <!-- <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="lightgrey" padding="10px 46px" /> -->
        <mj-spacer height="20px" />
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <h2 style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5">
            <strong>Fun Fact :</strong>
          </h2>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5">
            <strong>Can an eye color reveal your level of discomfort?</strong>
          </p>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5">
            Yes! Studies say light-eyed folks may tolerate pain better, while
            dark-eyed folks feel it intensely.
          </p>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5">
            But do you know another fact about dark-eyed people? They can handle
            alcohol better. Interesting, right?
          </p>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; filter: blur(5px)">
            So if you need an added shot next time, blame your eyes!
          </p>
        </mj-text>
        <!-- <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="lightgrey" padding="10px 46px" /> -->
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-spacer height="15px"></mj-spacer>
  </mj-body>
</mjml>
